Interface JJackAudioProcessorMonitorable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Cable, Channel, Delay, Gain, Gate, JJackClient, JJackMonitor, Oscilloscope, Socket, VU

    public interface JJackAudioProcessorMonitorable
    Extends interface JJackAudioProcessor by the ability to add listeners that get informed about starting and ending of processing.
    Version:
    0.3
    Author:
    Jens Gulden
